race.description: The Council Canter Country Boosted Hcp (C3)
race.comment: PONY SOPRANO (2) is a leader who folded up at Rosehill last time, but he'd been narrowly beaten there to outing prior. Has a gun hoop booked today and he will manage the gelding better. Draws to advantage and over shorter in the country will take beating. WHERE'STHEPROFIT (3) capped narrow defeats here with a CL2 win at Dubbo heavily supported again. Maps well and Morgan stays aboard. Has scope for further improvement and is a threat. LIGHTNING SPEED (6) was in the market at Randwick 37 days ago and pulled up with an issue. Won a 66 at Tamworth first-up prior and has been kept up to the mark with a narrow miss in a trial here. Has a low gate and claims.CRIMSON BONNET (11) brings a comfortable CL2 win from Tamworth over this distance and goes into the trifectas.
